reviewText: I did not know what was meant by region 2 and it is a worthless purchase because it does not play in my region which I have learned is 1 These dvd should not be allowed to be listed with region 1

Probably not vendor's fault but this international format will not play on either of my two DVD players.  I did not see any mention on the website but I was not looking as I assumed it was the USA format.
